        "TileImage": "$($repository 56e854bc-f006-4cc6-99d9-85fc6898901d).Image",
        "Description": "Agent 47, welcome to Whittleton Creek. your targets - Bobby Ashcraft, Gayle Pooley and Herbert West - are leading an uprising against Taylor Swift, aiming to crush her reputation. \r\rBobby, &quot;the archer&quot;, hides as a jealous garbage man and is in charge of their headquarters. \rGayle, a fiery mastermind, is spreading the rebellion.\rHerbert, a former employee of her merch store. He is trying to make a poison for her in his muffins. \r\rSilence them before their anti-hero plans take root. Good luck",
